    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In modern warfare, helmets for military use, especially those intended for the battlefield. Originally of metal, today also of Kevlar; usually provided with a suspension system or liner and chin strap.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
